name: Cow No.6 From the Mythologic Farm
description:
Mythologic cows have been created in several collections by the means of Softwares and its techniques. They have been personified based on ancient stories by Asoric Studio .

Get rich and make your future happy by buying each of these cows in Blockchain Market. 
In addition There would be no roadmap for the collections.
It’s Only you, that can make yourself rich.
The future displays everything
